name: CryptoNekos 01: Manekiss Neko
description:
Maneki Neko, is a popular Japanese sculpture that brings good luck, money, and clients to its owner.

In this project I decided to work on a syncretism combining popular Japanese sculpture and characters from Western pop culture.

This Neko is a tribute to the rock band Kiss, for their great music, but also for one of the comics that inspired me most when I was younger: Kiss Psycho Circus.

I still have it.
​

This Neko NFT will attract rhythm and rock your life!

more info: https://www.cryptonekos.com/
